'''Union of Cinema Production Workers''' ({{Lang-es|'''Sindicato de Trabajadores de la Producción Cinematográfica'''}}) was an autonomous (non-"[[Charro (Mexican politics)|charro]]"-led) [[Mexico|Mexican]] [[trade union]].  It was formed in 1944 after splitting off from the [[Confederation of Mexican Workers|CTM]]-affiliated [[Union of Cinema Industry Workers]] (''Sindicato de Trabajadores de la Industria Cinematográfica'', (STIC)).  Mario Moreno "[[Cantinflas]]" served as its first secretary general.<ref>{{cite web |url= https://www.proceso.com.mx/187361/el-sindicato-de-la-produccion-cinematografica-en-elecciones|title= el sindicato de la producción cinematográfica, en elecciones|author=<!--Not stated--> |date= 6 April 2002|website= proceso.com.mx|publisher= Proceso|access-date= 6 June 2018|quote=}}</ref>

